All five have been played at positions other than ADC with AD builds in the past year in the pros. Three have been in the past 1-2 months. Two were today. And, if you really want to be a Jinx one-trick, then learn her in other lanes. She might not be optimal, but that's why you learn her. I've been lately trying to one-trick Gnar. Am I raging on the Boards because the only thing he's meta on is top? No, I'm practicing my jungle clears and support skills.
